Package: statcanR
Type: Package
Title: An R Package to access Statistics Canada's Open economic Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person("Thierry", "Warin", email = "thierry.warin@skema.edu", role =c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Romain", "Le Duc", role = "aut"))
Description: The statcanR package allows an easy connection with R to Statistics Canada's Web Data Service. Open economic data (formerly known as CANSIM tables, now identified by Product IDs (PID)) are accessible as a data frame, directly in the user's R environment.
